md:
giải nghĩa từ "jen" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

Jen (n) - Unit of measurement

* Meaning: Đơn vị đo lường
* Part of speech: Noun
* Example sentence: "The recipe calls for 2 jens of sugar."
* Related words: measurement, unit, quantity
* Antonyms: none

Jen (v) - To make something more interesting or attractive

* Meaning: Làm cho cái gì đó trở nên hấp dẫn hơn
* Part of speech: Verb
* Example sentence: "The designer jenned up the website with some flashy graphics."
* Related words: enhance, improve, decorate
* Antonyms: dull, boring

Jen (adj) - Attractive or appealing

* Meaning: Hấp dẫn, hấp dẫn
* Part of speech: Adjective
* Example sentence: "The jen model walked down the catwalk with confidence."
* Related words: attractive, appealing, charming
* Antonyms: unattractive, unappealing

Note: The word "jen" is not a commonly used word in English, and its meanings may vary depending on the context. The above definitions are provided for reference purposes only.
